headline.print_headline: A's Pitcher Parker to Miss Season After Elbow Surgery
headline.main: A's Pitcher Parker to Miss Season After Elbow Surgery

lead_paragraph: Jarrod Parker, who was favored to be the Oakland Athletics' Opening Day starter entering spring training, will undergo elbow surgery and miss the Major League Baseball season, the team said on Monday.
